{"tid":1154843,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日個00後part-time請病假，今日返嚟俾我屌到跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-05-14T14:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T18:29:47.000Z","uid":150100,"like":23,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"32303087400482f60fdb5fd6814ee0d7daef023e","tid":1154843,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    00後:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：琴日做咩唔返工？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我病咗吖，返唔到，嗱依度有醫生紙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你行到去睇醫生點解返唔到工？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我&hellip;我&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n條廢柴即刻跪底流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n駁唔到嗱，偷懶就偷懶啦<br />\n你知唔知你咁唔負責任就咁唔返我地要做多幾多嘢<br />\n你地啲00後究竟食屎大定飲尿大<br />\n全部都廢柴嚟，冇撚柒閪用<br />\n俾人屌兩屌就喊到成隻豬<br />\n唔怪得之人人都話00後垃圾嚟<br />\n我一路屌，佢就一路趴喺塊地度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌到咁上下見佢都喊到窒息咁<br />\n下場馬又就開跑我先停，放佢一馬<br />\n反正啲垃圾都屌唔醒㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主冇做錯到"},{"pid":"3e1c9389252ad51baa44ae604c68a41f0aeb11da","tid":1154843,"uid":198113,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"69652d4c7c68a0766b735aca7e3a07b3924586e6","tid":1154843,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"起底 正負皮都唔㩒 上一頁"},{"pid":"4fca24e790f1acb05d6c91b945d045100f